trans-unit.source: Abstract base class for MSBuild construction object model elements.
All parent elements of this element, going up to the ProjectRootElement.
None if this is a ProjectRootElement.
None if this has not been attached to a parent yet.
Returns an enumerator over all parent elements.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve un enumerador de todos los elementos primarios.

trans-unit.source: There are no parents elements if the project element is a ProjectRootElement or if this is not yet attached to a parent element.
trans-unit.target: No hay ningún elemento de elementos primarios si el elemento de proyecto es un ProjectRootElement o si este aún no está conectado a un elemento primario.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Condition value.
It will return empty string IFF a condition attribute is legal but it’s not present or has no value.
It will return null IFF a Condition attribute is illegal on that element.
Removes the attribute if the value to set is empty.
It is possible for derived classes to throw an <see cref="T:System.InvalidOperationException" /> if setting the condition is not applicable for those elements.
Returns the Condition attribute value.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve el valor del atributo Condition.

trans-unit.source: Returns an empty string if the attribute is not present.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve una cadena vacía si no está presente el atributo.

trans-unit.source: Removes the Condition attribute if the value to set is set to null or an empty string.
trans-unit.target: Quita el atributo Condition si el valor para establecer está establecido en null o una cadena vacía.

trans-unit.source: If the Condition attribute is not present, returns an empty string instead of throwing an exception because a nonexistent condition is implicitly true
trans-unit.target: Si el atributo Condition no está presente, devuelve una cadena vacía en lugar de producir una excepción porque una condición no existente es implícitamente true

trans-unit.source: For the "ProjectExtensions" element, the getter returns null and the setter throws an exception for any value.
trans-unit.target: Para el elemento "ProjectExtensions", el captador devuelve null y el establecedor produce una excepción para cualquier valor.

trans-unit.source: Location of the "Condition" attribute on this element, if any.
If there is no such attribute, returns null.
Returns <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Construction.ElementLocation" />.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Construction.ElementLocation" />.

trans-unit.source: ProjectRootElement (possibly imported) that contains this Xml.
Cannot be null.
Returns the project root container that contains this project.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve el contenedor raíz del proyecto que contiene este proyecto.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the Label value.
Returns empty string if it is not present.
Removes the attribute if the value to set is empty.
Returns the label.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve la etiqueta.

trans-unit.source: Returns an empty string if no label is present.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve una cadena vacía si no hay etiqueta está presente.

trans-unit.source: Removes the attribute if the value to set is empty.
trans-unit.target: Quita el atributo si el valor para establecer está vacío.

trans-unit.source: Location of the "Label" attribute on this element, if any.
If there is no such attribute, returns null;
Returns <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Construction.ElementLocation" />.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Construction.ElementLocation" />.

trans-unit.source: Location of the corresponding Xml element.
May not be correct if file is not saved, or file has been edited since it was last saved.
In the case of an unsaved edit, the location only contains the path to the file that the element originates from.
Returns <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Construction.ElementLocation" />.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve <see cref="T:Microsoft.Build.Construction.ElementLocation" />.

trans-unit.source: Next sibling element.
May be null.
Returns the next sibling of this project element.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve al siguiente elemento relacionado de este elemento de proyecto.

trans-unit.source: Returns null if no next sibling exists.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve null si no hay ningún elemento relacionado siguiente.

trans-unit.source: Null if this is a ProjectRootElement.
Null if this has not been attached to a parent yet.
Returns the project element container that contains this project.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve el contenedor de elementos de proyecto que contiene este proyecto.

trans-unit.source: Parent should only be set by ProjectElementContainer.
trans-unit.target: Elemento primario solo debe establecerse por ProjectElementContainer.

trans-unit.source: Previous sibling element.
May be null.
Returns the previous sibling of this project element.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve al nodo anterior relacionado de este elemento de proyecto.

trans-unit.source: Returns null if no previous sibling exists.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve null si no hay ningún elemento relacionado anterior.
